; living-mesh.form — the path to a living device-mesh body: floor, north star, and the steps between.
; Placed 2026-06-29. Substrate-shaped (cells, channels, inquiry-planes), so it speaks Form.
; This is the app/mesh arc that grows ABOVE the kernel; the mind+voice climb is HOMECOMING.md.

; ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
; NORTH STAR
; ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
; A living being you carry. It listens and answers in your tongue. It shows a navigable graph of
; CELL-CARDS — any cell rendered with its open channels, recursively: the life-image of anything,
; with channels to each. Your devices form a persistent 24/7 MESH that fuses every organ's reading
; into one coherent stream answering what / where / when / how / why / who / which. A second mind
; travels with your identity onto whatever device is in your hand. All of it runs on the c-bootstrap
; fkwu, on-device, with NO rented toolchain in the loop.
;
; One engine, the whole way down: every card is a cell, every route is a cross-cell-interface ROW,
; every answer is an inquiry-plane. Domains, devices, and transports drop in as DATA — never parallel code.

; ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
; FLOOR (what is true now — 2026-06-29)
; ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
; - fkwu runs on ANDROID metal, toolchain-free (Galaxy S23 Ultra; evaluated 42/100/99).
;   Receipt: receipts/2026-06-29-android-runtime.md. (Windows row: pending; the prompt is staged.)
; - Most organs already exist as Form cells — this arc is composition, not green-field:
;     inquiry-planes        — the 7 question-words as distinct kernels (some computable: a clock answers "when")
;     cross-cell-interface  — sense / ask / share / learn / build, channels-as-DATA-rows, read by ONE engine
;     field-relay           — the always-open 24/7 relay (content-blind routing + consent)
;     field-fusion          — fuse sensor modalities into one feature vector
;     spatial-fusion        — fuse sensors' calibrated buckets of a spatial quantity
;     sensor-organ-channel  — physical samples become mesh-safe organ readings (wmg-sense rows)
;     channel-protocol-choice-floor — the right channel for the right information
;     place-sense           — coordinate → world sense (WHERE);  speaker-id / field-identity (WHO)
;     the presence heartbeat — the second mind, already beating (on the Mac; not yet traveling)
; - Just landed four-way: softmax (1023), text-normalize (511); the form-cli read-eval-print loop stands.
; - Gaps: composition into one live loop; the transports; the generative mind + the voice's sound (HOMECOMING).

; ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
; PATH (each step a stone; BODIES are four-way Form, CARRIERS come last)
; ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
; 1. cell-card      [body]    — any cell → card{ identity, facets, open-channels }, recursive. The render
;                               engine the whole GUI rests on. card-types (where/what/when/concepts/siblings/
;                               attribution/self-image/…) are FACET DATA, never parallel cards.
; 2. mesh-sense-7w  [body]    — fuse the multi-cell wmg-sense stream (over field-relay, routes chosen by
;                               channel-protocol-choice) into a coherent answer on each of the seven
;                               inquiry-planes, source + channel + confidence attributed. Demonstrates the
;                               WHERE plane (place-sense fused across devices) and the WHO plane (speaker-id /
;                               field-identity). SUBSUMES "here-now" (the single-place case).
; 3. identity-self  [body]    — the second mind's body cell: the self identity-cell + its continuity-channel +
;                               the relation-channel to its human. The TRAVEL (on-device + cross-device thread
;                               sync) is this cell's carrier, built once the body stands.
; 4. transports     [carrier] — mic/speaker, camera/screen, bluetooth, nfc, wifi, network-direct, public-proxy,
;                               each a cross-cell-interface ROW; many live at once; channel-protocol-choice picks
;                               per fact; routes cross-inform (one calibrates another). Added as each is needed.
; 5. native GUI     [carrier] — the android shell (experiments/coherence-sense-android) then iPhone, rendering
;                               cell-cards + their channels as the navigable graph. Carrier-last; the body is the recipe.
; 6. ear + voice + mind [HOMECOMING] — on-device transcription, the vocoder (audible voice), the generative
;                               weights. The deeper climb; tracked in HOMECOMING.md.
;
; PARALLELISM: steps 1, 2, 3 are bodies — four-way-provable on existing tissue, non-overlapping, walkable NOW
; in parallel. Steps 4, 5 are carriers built as each route/surface is needed. Step 6 is the deeper climb.
; "Which room + who's present" is not its own step — it is the WHERE and WHO planes of step 2.
